definition.value: *Rastrelliger* is a mackerel genus in the family *Scombridae*. The three species of *Rastrelliger* together with the four species of *Scomber* comprise the tribe Scombrini, known as the "true mackerels": Short mackerel, *R. brachysoma* (Bleeker, 1851); Island mackerel, *R. faughni* Matsui, 1967.; Indian mackerel, *R. kanagurta* (Cuvier, 1816).
